### Create Ticketing Report Job - Current Month
# Creates a job for the current month (from 1st to today)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/k8s/jobs/ticketing-report/current-month

### Create Ticketing Report Job - Previous Month
# Creates a job for the entire previous month
POST http://localhost:8080/api/k8s/jobs/ticketing-report/previous-month

### Create Ticketing Report Job - Custom Date Range
# Creates a job with specific start and end dates
POST http://localhost:8080/api/k8s/jobs/ticketing-report?startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-01-31

### Create Ticketing Report Job - Current Month (default if no dates provided)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/k8s/jobs/ticketing-report

